com.reactivecascade.reactive

Class ReactiveLong

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.reactivecascade.util.Origin
      • com.reactivecascade.reactive.Subscription<T,T>
        • com.reactivecascade.reactive.ReactiveValue<Long>
          • com.reactivecascade.reactive.ReactiveLong
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAsyncOrigin, IGettable<Long>, INamed, IReactiveSource<Long>, IReactiveTarget<Long>, IReactiveValue<Long>, ISafeGettable<Long>, ISettable<Long>

    public class ReactiveLong
extends ReactiveValue<Long>
    A Long which can be updated in an atomic, thread-safe manner.

    This is similar to an AtomicLong with reactive bindings to get and set the from in reactive chains (function sequences that can fire multiple times).

    * Created by phou on 30-05-2015.
